INSTALL

    # Get `BashByRef'
git clone git@github.com:fvue/BashByRef.git
    # Get submodule `bash-completion'
cd BashByRef && git submodule update --init


TEST SUITE

To run the tests:

    cd test
    ./runUnit

Example output:

    Test Run By me on Sun May 30 08:51:40 2010
    Native configuration is i686-pc-linux-gnu

